# Public release staging scope.
#
# At this stage, only the public documentation tree, public project tree, and
# root release metadata files are trackable. Top-level build, output, tool,
# scratch, and artifact directories are local preparation artifacts.
/*
!/docs/
!/project/
!/.gitignore
!/LICENSE
!/NOTICE
!/README.md

/build/
/build-*/
/cmake-build-*/
/output/
/artifacts/
/dist/
/release/
/tmp/
/tools/

CMakeCache.txt
CMakeFiles/
CTestTestfile.cmake
Testing/
*.o
*.obj
*.a
*.so
*.dylib
*.dll
*.exe
*.pdb
*.ilk
*.pyc
__pycache__/
.pytest_cache/
.cache/
.DS_Store
*.log
*.tmp
*.swp

# Donor material in the public repository is limited to original regression
# suites and compiled/downloaded tool harness payloads. Donor source trees,
# source archives, release-packet evidence extracts, and source-acquisition
# manifests stay local/private and must not be tracked.
project/tests/donor_regression/donor_release_acquisition/**
!project/tests/donor_regression/donor_release_acquisition/
!project/tests/donor_regression/donor_release_acquisition/**/
!project/tests/donor_regression/donor_release_acquisition/**/regression/
!project/tests/donor_regression/donor_release_acquisition/**/regression/**

!project/tests/donor_regression/donor_catalog_seeds/
!project/tests/donor_regression/donor_catalog_seeds/**
!project/tests/donor_regression/**/native_tool_harness/tools/
!project/tests/donor_regression/**/native_tool_harness/tools/**
!project/tests/donor_regression/firebird/original_firebird_qa/
!project/tests/donor_regression/firebird/original_firebird_qa/**
